{"tid":1633294,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"好似輸其實贏","createTime":"2019-10-07T03:20:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:37:09.000Z","uid":296447,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9e42a1b3579b2f82e8f12c845c947467605406ed","tid":1633294,"uid":296447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:20:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">文宣來了。<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n要大量上載在蒙面法後<br />\n<br />\n示威者在昨天被黑警打的相，<br />\n大學被狗入侵捉大學生，<br />\n幾個細佬被捉時淚如雨下，<br />\n一家三口有小朋友坐在單車上被黑警指非法集會，<br />\n一個示威者被捕後被黑警不斷打，<br />\n黑警扮示威者破壞物件後返回警車。</span><br />\n<br />\n未來十天，就是要比國際睇到這些。<br />\n<br />\nP 牌推不起，請幫手。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"9c18a2656cdd5fe6003e5279e7c7439185109436","tid":1633294,"uid":296447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:21:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">自推</span></span>"},{"pid":"d1c1942e2ff7101b88dc7c892b9118617b5d4c8f","tid":1633294,"uid":296447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:21:29.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8fcbdcdb6f092c71c7adbad40296bc6b138d1920","tid":1633294,"uid":296447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:21:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b789045354616d5f7dfffbd368f315e96d70ca40","tid":1633294,"uid":41314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:31:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bd4147610fb53f51557ac983fa6af2a8fcc9d28f","tid":1633294,"uid":101750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:32:28.000Z","msg":"全民文宣呀"},{"pid":"26be0940e963bbdf02177dbfa71468be6affa476","tid":1633294,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:25:08.000Z","msg":"啱呀, 快幫手"},{"pid":"011762ab67010a545a9d738331515d60010a22d7","tid":1633294,"uid":296447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:09:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ff6ba612cd97cf483244af